            'inter-header' => 'International collaboration',
            'inter-text-1' => 'Falsterbo fågelstation has signed a formal friendship agreement between us, <a href="https://njaudubon.org/centers/cape-may-bird-observatory/">New Jersey Audubon\'s Cape May Bird Observatory</a> (USA), <a href="https://www.birdscanada.org/longpoint/">Long Point Bird Observatory</a> (Kanada) och <a href="https://www.spurnbirdobservatory.co.uk/">Spurn Bird Observatory</a> (UK). The aim with this agreement is to promote international collaboration to stimulate increased environmental awareness.',
